THE GIRL FROM UNCLE -1x05- THE MONTORI DEVICE AFFAIR  (10/11/66)

THRUSH agents attack an UNCLE outpost in Rome and make off with a Montori device. With this device in their possession all of UNCLE&#039;s transmissions are compromised. Conrad Rossano, a famous fashion designer, is UNCLE&#039;s chief suspect. April goes undercover as a fashion buyer and Mark as an American bodyguard to a high price fashion model. Also involved is a Professor with a brain washing device which leaves the victim susceptible to his suggestions.
